{"tid":871671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北角利都樓高層兩房700萬沽 創物業新高","createTime":"2018-10-22T06:48:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T07:20:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3bd9e7b698ba41d4176c63cbacf280471f10ff","tid":871671,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"二手市場觀望氣氛未見改善，個別優質單位卻逆市錄新高成交。世紀21北山地產營業董事嚴智贇表示，新近錄得北角英皇道177至191A號利都樓成交，單位為高層I室，實用面積501平方呎，2房間隔，座向西面享海景，獲區外上車客以700萬元承接，實用面積呎價13,972元，造價及呎價創該物業歷史新高。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，原業主於2009年8月購入上址自住，當時作價238萬元，持貨至今沽售，帳面獲利462萬元，單位9年升值逾1.9倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2188306/%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E5%88%A9%E9%83%BD%E6%A8%93%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF700%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%20%E5%89%B5%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2188306%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2588%25BF700%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25B2%25BD%2520%25E5%2589%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598&d=hOZCSuynYZfFE9uXVR4tkXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=43c57c72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2188306/%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E5%88%A9%E9%83%BD%E6%A8%93%E9%AB%98%E5%B1%A4%E5%85%A9%E6%88%BF700%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%20%E5%89%B5%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98</a>"},{"pid":"61182f6b054bad1b7fe0714f53511cf31d91709d","tid":871671,"uid":19927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"港島唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c993170e815cc2f8bd14ceae5507d295120cf4af","tid":871671,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T07:12:59.000Z","msg":"港島都係$14000尺 重要有海景 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪之得創新高